El Toro Mexican Grill is definitely a GEM in the Financial District. I came here once and ever since my first time here, I've come at least twice a week.  If I don't bring lunch to work, You'll find me here on my lunch time. I could even eat the same dish every day and would not make me get tired of eating the same thing cause the food is incredibly delicious, tasteful, perfectly cooked and put together.  I love it here!!!!!!!!! I usually get a Taco Salad, either chicken or steak, BOTH are incredibly delightful. In my opinion the Nachos are THE BOMB, but they are too big for an average person. It is, although, a perfect option for sharing with somebody else.  For those with a PASSIONATE and HIGH LOVE for meat, this is your place. They are DEFINITELY NOT shy AT ALL with MEAT portions, THE BEST PART, in my opinion. I'M A PROTEIN LOVER!!!!!!!!  The staff is lovely, always smiling, always helping you make bad choices as for food. Simple a GREAT atmosphere as a whole!!!!!  El Toro (Not Loco) is 500% recommended. AWESOME!!!!!!! LOVE IT!!!
